Version: 1.0
ProjectId: bf22a446-3320-4121-ac26-cafa1897c284

RestoreWorkspace: No
SaveWorkspace: No
AlwaysSaveHistory: Yes

EnableCodeIndexing: Yes
UseSpacesForTab: Yes
NumSpacesForTab: 2
Encoding: UTF-8
AutoAppendNewline: Yes

RnwWeave: Sweave
LaTeX: pdfLaTeX

StripTrailingWhitespace: Yes

BuildType: None
PackageUseDevtools: Yes
PackageInstallArgs: --no-multiarch --with-keep.source
